'''Force call''' was a powerful [[Force power/Legends|Force technique]] utilized by only a few [[Force-sensitive/Legends|Force-sensitives]], due to the amount of energy required to use this power.

Utilizing [[The Force/Legends|the Force]], a [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] could call other Jedi to his or her position; this amounted to a shout that echoed throughout the Force itself. For those who heard this summons, it would be nearly impossible to resist. [[Raynar Thul]] used this to summon the survivors of the [[Myrkr strike team]] at the beginning of the Dark Nest Crisis, while [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] used this technique on Ossus for a [[Conclave on Ossus|Convocation]] of the [[New Jedi Order]] shortly before the end of the war.

